♪Gazing at the returning swallows♪

5
00:01:07,348 --> 00:01:13,428
♪The seasons swiftly come and go♪

6
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:16,320
Give it to me.

7
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,560
Turn around.

8
00:01:21,897 --> 00:01:28,582
♪Like a love poem, endlessly extending♪

9
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:39,560
Alright.

10
